Summaries:

Hosea 14;
	
	Talking about how god wants the people to come back and that god's ways are right
and should be followed.

Jeremiah 24:4-7;

	god saying that god will bring them back, that god wants us to thrive not be 
'torn' down.

Nehemiah  9:30,31;

	that god is merciful and loves us, and will not abondon us.

Joel 2:13;

	god loves us/cares for us and we should be 'with' god. will not try to do things 
that will cause harm.

Nehemiah 9:16,17;

	god is forgiving and that you should not leave god and that god does not 
desert you/them.
